text: James Matthew Teng, (born on February 3, 1998 in Marilao, Bulacan, Philippines), is a Filipino teen actor and model who rose to fame in the sixth season of StarStruck. He is currently seen and has a semi-exclusive contract on GMA Network. == Career and personal life == Teng just graduated high school before joining StarStruck. He already works as a model. His list of hobbies includes guitar and basketball. He is the nephew of the Basketball Legend Alvin Teng and the cousin of Jeric Teng and Jeron Teng.
